headline: Textron Aviation Expands ProAdvantage Portfolio With Launch of ProParts+ for Cessna Citation 525 Series
summary: WICHITA, Kan., September 02, 2025--Textron Aviation announced the launch of ProParts+ program, designed specifically for Cessna Citation 525 series operators.

headline: Gabelli Funds to Host 31st Annual Aerospace & Defense Symposium at The Harvard Club, New York City Thursday, September 4, 2025
summary: GREENWICH, Conn., Sept. 02, 2025 (GLOBE NEWSWIRE) -- Gabelli Funds, LLC, is hosting our annual Aerospace & Defense Symposium at The Harvard Club in New York City on September 4th. The conference will draw top executives from more than ten companies, with a focus on the themes of strong demand outlook, high barriers to entry, large aftermarket opportunity, growth in excess of GDP, defense spending, and M&A potential for the Aerospace and Defense industry.
